Name: Planes, Trains, and Automobiles
Description:
Songs about the following types of vehicles:
Planes, Trains, and Automobiles.

So really, any song where a vehicle is a key part of the song!

Name: No (Six) Strings Attached
Description:
Songs without guitars. I'm going to be really upset with you if you post with one.

SO DON'T.

Name: Let Me Put This Into A Language You'll Understand
Description:
So for this one, I want you to submit a song in a language.

Here's some ideas of languages:
Spanish
Mandarin
Portuguese
Japanese
Hindi
Arabic
Russian
German
Korean
French

Here's one you can't pick:
English

So. Something not in English.

Name: Amoeba Music
Description: Music for microbes. So to elaborate, music that sounds strange, alien, evocative of the single-celled organisms referred to as Amoebas. This is up to interpretation.
